<br>
Do all of you know there are THREE OTHER WAYS to get spells right? I'm gonna repeat that just in case y'all missed it.<br>
<br>
THREE OTHER WAYS<br>
<br>
Three quest ways. Off 3 NPCs. One wants us to extract the spells from items that have charges of the spells in them, another wants us to combine new runes/pages/components to make new spells (like the old days) and the final one wants us to combine old spells to make new ones. Myself and a few other people are wracking our brains on these new spells and could use the collective brainpower of the rest of you mages out there to get thinking! See the other threads (one is even STICKIED) and burn some grey matter. This is why Verant will not up the drop rate on parchments, because it is only supposed to constitute 1/4 of the total spells. <br>
<br>
I personally am partial to the quest about combining older spells, and am trying to make serious headway on that one. However, the entire caster community seems to be stumped. So, help out! <br>
<br>
